snippet.title: EverQuest Worlds Mobile App [OFFICIAL TRAILER]
snippet.description:
Download for free on Iphone: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/id680...
Download for free on Android:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/de...

EverQuest Worlds keeps you up-to-date with everything happening in the EverQuest Franchise...including Landmark. Complete quests for great in-game rewards, play fun mini-games, and get your franchise news and videos on the go!

Original music by Jeremy Soule
